      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/22/2/16/12",
      "text": [
        ": سألته عن القائم ، فقال: كذب الوقاتون، إنا أهل بيت لا نوقت. ثم قال: أبى الله إلاّ أن يخلف وقت الموقتين."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.abdullah-al-shahin": [
          "(12) Muhammad bin Ya’qoob narrated from some of his teachers from Ahmad bin Muhammad bin Khalid from his father from Ali Abu Hamza that Abu Baseer had asked Abu Abdullah as-Sadiq (as) about al-Qa’im (as) and he said: “The diviners tell lies. We, Ahlul Bayt, do not time. Allah dose not consent save to reverse the timing of the diviners.”"
        ]
      }
    },
